issue.body:
To me the docs are unclear about whether I have to do this:

```js
FooComponent.propTypes = {
    children: propTypes.oneOfType([
        instanceOfComponent(BarComponent),
        propTypes.arrayOf(instanceOfComponent(BarComponent)),
    ]),
}
```

Of if the following will already cover that case:
```js
FooComponent.propTypes = {
    children: instanceOfComponent(BarComponent),
}
```

