I like to take `lodash/fp`s `isEqual function and do this in my personal projects:

```js
import { isEqual } from 'lodash/fp'

const reducer = (state, { type, payload }) => {
  const isType = isEqual(type)

  if (isType(ACTION_TYPE)) {
    return ...
  }

  return state
}
```

